question: List therapies with variant-level biomarkers in Lung Squamous Cell Carcinoma.
cypher:
MATCH (v:Variant)-[rel:AFFECTS_RESPONSE_TO]->(t:Therapy)
WHERE (
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'lung' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'squamous' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'cell' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'carcinoma'
  )
OPTIONAL MATCH (v)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
RETURN
  v.name AS variant_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  rel.effect AS effect,
  rel.disease_name AS disease_name,
  coalesce(rel.pmids, []) AS pmids
LIMIT 100

MATCH (v:Variant)-[rel:AFFECTS_RESPONSE_TO]->(t:Therapy)
WHERE (
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'ureter' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'small' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'cell' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'carcinoma'
  )
OPTIONAL MATCH (v)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
RETURN
  v.name AS variant_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  rel.effect AS effect,
  rel.disease_name AS disease_name,
  coalesce(rel.pmids, []) AS pmids
LIMIT 100

MATCH (v:Variant)-[rel:AFFECTS_RESPONSE_TO]->(t:Therapy)
WHERE (
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'anaplastic' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'ependymoma'
  )
OPTIONAL MATCH (v)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
RETURN
  v.name AS variant_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  rel.effect AS effect,
  rel.disease_name AS disease_name,
  coalesce(rel.pmids, []) AS pmids
LIMIT 100

MATCH (v:Variant)-[rel:AFFECTS_RESPONSE_TO]->(t:Therapy)
WHERE (
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'medullary' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'thyroid' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'carcinoma'
  )
OPTIONAL MATCH (v)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
RETURN
  v.name AS variant_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  rel.effect AS effect,
  rel.disease_name AS disease_name,
  coalesce(rel.pmids, []) AS pmids
LIMIT 100

MATCH (v:Variant)-[rel:AFFECTS_RESPONSE_TO]->(t:Therapy)
WHERE (
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'myofibroma'
  )
OPTIONAL MATCH (v)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
RETURN
  v.name AS variant_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  rel.effect AS effect,
  rel.disease_name AS disease_name,
  coalesce(rel.pmids, []) AS pmids
LIMIT 100

    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'b-cell' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'lymphoma' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'activated' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'b-cell' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'type'
  )
OPTIONAL MATCH (v)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
RETURN
  v.name AS variant_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  rel.effect AS effect,
  rel.disease_name AS disease_name,
  coalesce(rel.pmids, []) AS pmids
LIMIT 100

WHERE (
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'extraskeletal' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'myxoid' AND
    toLower(rel.disease_name) CONTAINS 'chondrosarcoma'
  )
OPTIONAL MATCH (v)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
RETURN
  v.name AS variant_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  rel.effect AS effect,
  rel.disease_name AS disease_name,
  coalesce(rel.pmids, []) AS pmids
LIMIT 100
